<section id="work" class="section-padding"
    style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #050505, #0a0a0a); content-visibility: auto; contain-intrinsic-size: 80vh;">
    <div class="container">
        <div
            style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: end; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">
            <h2 class="animate-on-scroll" style="font-size: 3rem;">Client Results</h2>
            <p class="animate-on-scroll" style="color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 300px;">Don't just take our
                word for it. Here is what
                7-figure store owners are saying.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
            <!-- Sample Review 1 -->
            <div class="testimonial-card glass-card animate-on-scroll" style="padding: 2.5rem;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <div class="client-info">
                        <div class="client-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a, #3b82f6); width: 60px; height: 60px;"></div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.1rem;">Alex M.</h4>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">CEO, Urban Thread</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); color: #3b82f6; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700;">VERIFIED CLIENT</div>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text" style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; color: #fff;">"The Solian Wolves didn't just 'fix' our site. They completely overhauled our funnel. Conversions are up 45% in just two months."</p>
                <div style="color: #3b82f6; margin-top: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 2px;">★★★★★</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Sample Review 2 -->
            <div class="testimonial-card glass-card animate-on-scroll" style="padding: 2.5rem;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <div class="client-info">
                        <div class="client-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000, #1a1a1a); width: 60px; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; color: #3b82f6;">SJ</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.1rem;">Sarah Jenkins</h4>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Founder, Glow Cosmetics</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); color: #3b82f6; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700;">VERIFIED CLIENT</div>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text" style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; color: #fff;">"Our site speed was killing our ads. They did a deep audit, found the bloat, and now we load in under a second."</p>
                <div style="color: #3b82f6; margin-top: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 2px;">★★★★★</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Sample Review 3 -->
            <div class="testimonial-card glass-card animate-on-scroll" style="padding: 2.5rem;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <div class="client-info">
                        <div class="client-avatar" style="background: #3b82f6; width: 60px; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff;">TP</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.1rem;">TechGear Pro</h4>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">E-com Manager</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); color: #3b82f6; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700;">VERIFIED CLIENT</div>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text" style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; color: #fff;">"Professional, fast, and high-end code. It doesn't look like a template anymore. It looks like a real brand."</p>
                <div style="color: #3b82f6; margin-top: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 2px;">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

